track_notes: Easy hike up to the top.

3.75 mile loop hike with 1600 of EG/EL.  The summit is roughly half way going either direction so take your pick.  Summit is a very small area but I still chose to set up there since this is a popular hiking destination, but the summit is not visited much.  Large parking lot (36.1047, -83.7626) and overflow parking just down the road, but it is probably very crowded on the weekends.  Even on a Wednesday morning the main parking lot was pretty full.
